OL,3,CJudge issues directions in trial of
OL,4,Cman accused of murdering pensioner in
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FJurors must decide whether a Moroccan
OL,8,Fman who fatally stabbed a pensioner in
OL,9,Fthe street intended to kill or cause
OL,10,Freally serious harm, a judge said.
OL,12,FAhmed Alid, 45, is charged with
OL,13,Fmurdering Terence Carney, 70, in
OL,14,FHartlepool town centre, minutes after
OL,15,Frepeatedly knifing his sleeping
OL,16,Fhousemate Javed Nouri, 31, in his bed.
OL,18,FHe has , and indicated he was "scared"
OL,19,Fof Mr Nouri during the struggle in his
OL,20,Fhousemate's room.
