OL,7,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb told jurors
OL,8,Fthere was no defence of diminished
OL,9,Fresponsibility for Alid, and he could
OL,10,Fnot claim self-defence in respect of
OL,11,Fstabbing Mr Nouri.
OL,13,FShe said: "The only defence is that
OL,14,Fthe defendant did not intend to kill
OL,15,FJaved Nouri and he did not intend to
OL,16,Fkill or cause really serious harm to
OL,17,FTerence Carney.
OL,19,F"The only issue for you to determine
OL,20,Fis what harm he intended, if any, and
OL,21,Fyou must focus on that issue."
