OL,7,FThe prosecution has told Teesside
OL,8,FCrown Court that Alid, who was born in
OL,9,FMorocco and who moved around Europe
OL,10,Ffor years, was seeking "revenge" for
OL,11,Fthe Israel-Palestine conflict.
OL,13,FHe admits stabbing both men in the
OL,14,Fearly hours of 15 October last year,
OL,15,Feight days after Hamas launched their
OL,16,Fattacks on Israel, but denies murder
OL,17,Fand attempted murder.
