OL,4,Cman accused of murdering pensioner in
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FIn his closing speech to the jury,
OL,8,FJonathan Sandiford KC, prosecuting,
OL,9,Freminded the jury of CCTV footage
OL,10,Fwhich he said showed Alid did not
OL,11,Fcarry out a "frenzied attack".
OL,13,FInstead, Mr Sandiford said, Alid kept
OL,14,Fmoving to keep himself in front of Mr
OL,15,FCarney, so he could keep stabbing him
OL,16,Fin the body.
OL,18,FMr Sandiford asked: "Why do you think
OL,19,Fthat is, other than he was trying to
OL,20,Fdo the maximum damage, to kill him, as
OL,21,Findeed he did?"
