OL,7,FJohn Elvidge KC, defending, asked the
OL,8,Fjury to clear Alid of attempted murder
OL,9,Fand to convict him of the alternative
OL,10,Fcharge of wounding Mr Nouri, and clear
OL,11,Fhim of murdering Mr Carney in favour
OL,12,Fof the alternative charge of
OL,13,Fmanslaughter.
OL,15,FThe case was adjourned until Thursday
OL,16,Fwhen the judge will sum up the case
OL,17,Fbefore sending the jury out to
OL,18,Fconsider their verdicts.
